Jason Lee

Jason Michael Lee (* 25 April 1970– ) is 'n Oscar-bekroonde Amerikaanse komediant en akteur. Hy was veral bekend vir sy rol in "My Name Is Earl" (2005-2009), "The Incredibles" (2004), "Underdog" (2007), "Alvin and the Chipmunks" (2007), "Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel" (2009), en "Alvin and the Chipmunks: Chipwrecked" (2011).


